{"tid":2005282,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"第一次試用阿婆底褲cu銅芯口罩 其實我是拒絕的！","createTime":"2020-05-07T04:10:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T04:12:04.000Z","uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9a51ff67fa2696ee0004473c2ea2d908fdce514f","tid":2005282,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:10:01.000Z","msg":"呀&hellip;&hellip;當我第一次知道要拍那個阿婆底褲cu銅芯口罩的時候，其實我是拒絕的！因為我覺得&hellip;&hellip;呀&hellip;&hellip;你不能叫我戴、馬上戴，第一，我要試一下，我又不想說&hellip;&hellip;<del>你拍一個廣告拍完以後加了很多特技，那頭髮動啊&hellip;&hellip;很黑！很亮！很柔！結果觀眾出來一定罵我，根本沒有這種頭髮！這證明上面那個是假的&hellip;&hellip;我說先要給我試一下。後來我經過也知道他們是中藥的，而且沒有那種化學成分的。那&hellip;&hellip;洗了這個月&hellip;&hellip;這個月下來之後呢&hellip;&hellip;起碼我用了很舒服。現在呢&hellip;&hellip;每天還在用！每天還在用呢&hellip;&hellip;我還給了我成家班用！來！來！來！大家試試看！那我跟導演講︰「拍的時候就拍！拍完之後，這個頭髮就是我的頭髮，就不要加，再加特技上去，加到沒有就是這樣子！我要給觀眾看到，我用完之後是這樣子，你們用完之後，也是這樣子！ </del>"},{"pid":"ff29a658dec19f7e040eada86cada5d60dedc021","tid":2005282,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:10:30.000Z","msg":"有冇人幫手改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b25d056b20f235f8c6ee296d7d3592b6b345322","tid":2005282,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:12:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1nVjGTs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1nVjGTs.jpg&h=87486c74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YV3AZE9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYV3AZE9.png&h=dcd15af3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n上j圖比你 幫手改 全能既連登仔<img s